title: RUSSIAN DOLL Ending and Timeline Explained!
author: Think Story
comment: Thanks for watching everyone! This vid mainly focused on the ending and timeline but if you want to learn more like the meaning of "Russian Doll" or what the heck was up with "Emily of New Moon" you can check out Screenrant's article here: https://screenrant.com/russian-doll-netflix-ending-explained-time-loop/3/
I liked this very much, yet at the same time I kind of hope there isn't a season 2. It felt complete and resolved. It was less like a tv series and more like a long movie.
gotta get up, gotta get out

I really liked this series and I think it's worth watching twice just so you can see the differences you didnt see in the first run through. I think it was really well made and it was something new. Perfect for groundhog day too Haha!
That didn't "explain" anything. It was just a synopsis of the plot.
description:
Netflix's "Russian Doll" is a mind bending dramedy with a lot to unpack. In this video I explain the ending and the timeline which kept Nadia and Alan in a perpetual loop.
